data.meta_description: Hooked is a 14 year old  by Casino Prince out of the Lure mare, Absolute Lure. He has had 37 race starts for 6 wins with the latest being 2622 days ago when 14th at Doomben in the Stradbroke Hcp over 1350 metres.
data.text:
Hooked is a 14 year old by Casino Prince out of the Lure mare, Absolute Lure.

Last start was 14th at Doomben on June 10, 2017 in the Stradbroke Hcp (Gr.1) over 1350 metres.
